{
  "stem": "22883.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we could hear through the walls what they sometimes, under, you know, the influence of vodka were talking or saying or screaming and so and so.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was definite [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] instances that we heard that they were spreading on me and calling me, oh, special-- using special words.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I recognized right away they are assuming that I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not my wife Lilian, but me, personally me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So after I think a month of being there, we felt to be endangered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's-- the situation sometimes will be very-- very critical.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had-- we agreed-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Lilka and me-- Lilian and me, we agreed that we have to get out of this place.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's impossible to stay here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So during one of visit to-- to this office, of this German soldier's office, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] actually, that's-- she was that brave person-- did something which saved us later.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Apparently, there was-- all the time, there was a traffic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of my duties was to-- to report to those Germans that somebody has to go back to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for that reason, he had to have a-- a-- a document, of-- travel document.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those travel documents were given by those Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only with this travel document, you could travel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Apparently, those Polish workers, they didn't come to that place in order to-- to work for Germans or something like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was precedence.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because they were coming to this place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This region was cultivating tobacco.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were working for a few days or weeks and then finding some reason to go back to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at the same time, they were transporting loads of tobacco.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was the black market of tobacco.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
